Required Perl modules:

Text::Markup,
Git::Repository,
Config::Tiny

HTTP::Server::Brick if you are want to run test web server

Install from cpan:

	localhost@localdomain # cpan
	cpan shell -- CPAN exploration and modules installation (v1.9800)
	Enter 'h' for help.

	cpan[1]> notest force install MODULE::NAME

Try find it in repository in you distributive. 